  "description_snippet": "When the renderFrameHost commits to an error page[1], if the renderFrameHost is not live[2], the NavigationRequest will be destroyed.  \nThen the UAF will be triggered when returning to call the function PopulateDocumentTokenForCrossDocumentNavigation[3] and access the member variables.  \n  \n```  \nvo"
